name: XProc-Z
tagline: A platform for XProc web proxying (and other) applications.
body:
### XProc-Z

By Conal Tuohy (@Conal-Tuohy)

XProc-Z is a platform for hosting web applications written in the XProc language.

Download a release of XProc-Z as a [Java Web Application Archive (WAR file)](https://github.com/Conal-Tuohy/XProc-Z/releases).
